title: Jocko Podcast 16 - With Echo Charles | Machete Season
description:
Join the conversation:  @jockowillink , @echocharles , www.facebook.com/JockoPodcast

0:00:00 – Opening

1:50:05 – Dealing with training troops in hard and tragic situations.

1:57:27 – Advice on workout schedule with newborn kids.

2:16:12 – What are the right questions to ask?
